00:01:31.496 --> 00:01:32.915
"A is for apple."

00:01:34.421 --> 00:01:35.845
"A is for apple."

00:01:37.528 --> 00:01:42.216
"A is for apple" is for that child
in that part of the world

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:43.972
where apples grow out;

00:01:44.751 --> 00:01:46.727
who has an apple in her lunch bag;

00:01:48.235 --> 00:01:51.637
who goes to the grocery store
with her mom and sees red,

00:01:51.661 --> 00:01:55.314
green, yellow -- apples
of all shapes and colors and sizes.

00:01:56.049 --> 00:01:58.938
And so, introducing
education to this child

00:01:58.962 --> 00:02:01.084
with an alphabet sheet like this